    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按住上升，松开下潜。避开无数障碍，击败强大的Boss，夺回你的家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聆听我们的原创音轨，一边收集种子购买所有服装，一边时尚作战！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21世纪，这个国家成为了我们时代最大灾难之一的舞台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演路易，一条在充满敌意的世界中为一顿均衡饭菜而战的虫子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/9f7a96326e19039e0e518e535c001f29.poster.avif?t=1768273444\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/9f7a96326e19039e0e518e535c001f29.webm?t=1768273444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/9f7a96326e19039e0e518e535c001f29.mp4?t=1768273444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>世界是甜的——但也可能是酸的</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >橙子、奇异果、苹果……这个热带天堂中的每一份馈赠，对那些敢于为午餐而起的生物来说，都是致命威胁。逃离危险，到达终点，与水果Boss展开战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/c6e87eff90fe8cd67427f4e8b84dc327.poster.avif?t=1768273444\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/c6e87eff90fe8cd67427f4e8b84dc327.webm?t=1768273444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/c6e87eff90fe8cd67427f4e8b84dc327.mp4?t=1768273444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为属于你的东西而战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你以为电锯和投派机是苹果内部最可怕的东西？这些水果是有主人的——而他们可不喜欢分享。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/99240a1b82ae3a9dea053354b7f71938.poster.avif?t=1768273444\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/99240a1b82ae3a9dea053354b7f71938.webm?t=1768273444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/99240a1b82ae3a9dea053354b7f71938.mp4?t=1768273444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为最耀眼的那一个</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种子就像黄金，在这个世界里，黄金可以买来风格。解锁路易的全部服装，穿上属于你的荣耀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/4b702f07aa3888f899d6fdda9c341226.poster.avif?t=1768273444\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/4b702f07aa3888f899d6fdda9c341226.webm?t=1768273444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281650/extras/4b702f07aa3888f899d6fdda9c341226.mp4?t=1768273444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
